@startuml
title Builder - Ejemplo 2 - solucion para consultas SQL dinamicas
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class SqlQuery {
    +toString(): String
  }
  class SqlQueryBuilder {
    +select(String columns): SqlQueryBuilder
    +from(String table): SqlQueryBuilder
    +where(String condition): SqlQueryBuilder
    +orderBy(String column): SqlQueryBuilder
    +build(): SqlQuery
  }
}

SqlQueryBuilder ..> SqlQuery : crea
Main ..> SqlQuery : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
